90
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:27,460
Sir.

91
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,410
My fault. I'll go home now.

92
00:04:29,990 --> 00:04:30,830
I'll go with you.

93
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:32,170
Gao Tianyang, sit down.

94
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:36,750
Jiang Tian, you take
Sheng Wang downstairs.

95
00:04:43,290 --> 00:04:44,700
Sir, I'll go then.

96
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:49,750
Okay. Focus here. Let's continue.

97
