I've sent you the recordings
of the classes.

99
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:02,450
Don't forget to listen to
and review them.

100
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,750
Okay.

101
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:06,410
You don't need to take this week's test,

102
00:05:06,410 --> 00:05:08,330
but there will be
another one when you return,

103
00:05:08,330 --> 00:05:09,620
so you still need to study.

104
00:05:09,620 --> 00:05:10,830
Got it, Sheng Wang?

105
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,910
Got it. Thank you, sir.

106
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,410
You should thank Jiang Tian.

107
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,950
He reminded us to record the classes.

108
00:05:17,250 --> 00:05:18,250
Oh...

109
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,700
Even though you're family,

110
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:22,540
you should still thank your brother.

111
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,410
Understand?

112
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,200
Yeah, I got it.

113
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,200
Bye, sir.

114
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:31,080
May I come in?

115
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,200
Oh, sure.

116
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,160
Wang,

117
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:39,250
