137
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,290
Really, it's okay, Ms. Jiang.

138
00:06:28,290 --> 00:06:29,540
It's just my ankle that hurts.

139
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:30,910
Everything else is fine.

140
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:33,830
Alright then.

141
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,580
Have a good rest.

142
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:36,830
Eat more fruit.

143
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,670
Yeah.

144
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:39,790
If you need anything,

145
00:06:39,790 --> 00:06:41,120
just call me.

146
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,450
I'll be here to help.

147
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:43,660
Oh, sure.

148
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:51,750
Hey, Ms. Jiang.

149
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:56,340
Ms. Jiang...

150
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:01,120
Your phone.

151
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:03,450
Ms. Jiang,

152
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,040
