153
00:07:07,660 --> 00:07:09,450
I know you're doing this

154
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:12,160
because you miss Jiang Tian.

155
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:13,870
But I want to let you know,

156
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:16,330
Tian is doing really well in the dorm.

157
00:07:17,290 --> 00:07:19,950
I don't know what happened
between you two before,

158
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,330
but he's pretty happy now

159
00:07:22,330 --> 00:07:23,540
and doesn't blame you.

160
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:26,750
He thinks that as long as you're okay,

161
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,040
