162
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,410
And if you and my dad are okay,

163
00:07:30,410 --> 00:07:31,790
I'll be happy.

164
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,120
Thank you.

165
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,830
I told my dad about this before.

166
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,410
