167
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,700
We're family.

168
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,160
Thank you, Wang.

169
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,700
Wang, we're heading out now.

170
00:08:34,370 --> 00:08:36,160
Take care of yourself, alright?

171
00:08:38,010 --> 00:08:41,960
♪Hidden in your mysterious smile♪

172
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:47,610
