174
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:58,080
♪I want to know all your secrets♪

175
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:06,070
♪Until I find out the gap between us♪

176
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:10,740
♪And don't want to let you get hurt♪

177
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:16,820
♪I silently promised myself♪

178
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:22,090
♪That I would let you go with a smile♪

179
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:29,800
