♪A line crafted in solitude
just for you♪

181
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:39,160
♪It's okay. I'll be with you♪

182
00:09:39,310 --> 00:09:46,290
♪Until the last note
of the final melody♪

183
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:54,090
♪It's alright.
I'll hide my vulnerability♪

184
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:59,370
♪So you won't see that side of me♪

185
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:03,550
♪In those few minutes
of so-called destiny♪

186
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:07,590
♪It gives me severe pain each time♪

187
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,690
♪Right after saying goodbye♪

188
