215
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:20,200
It's a secret.

216
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,120
A secret?

217
00:12:21,230 --> 00:12:22,080
What about you?

218
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:25,080
Do you wanna go to Room 208
for some charcoal hot pot?

219
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:27,040
I don't have time.

220
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,200
No time?

221
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,370
Hot pot?

222
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,050
Isn't the power out?

223
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,500
Oh, you're using a small stove?

224
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:37,950
You know we aren't allowed
to use that stuff in the dorm.

225
00:12:37,950 --> 00:12:39,250
Shh!

226
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,000
Shi,

227
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,370
it's a secret.

228
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:44,000
Alright, a secret.

229
00:12:44,620 --> 00:12:45,870
Tian, do you wanna go to Room 208...

230
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:46,750
No.

231
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:47,950
But since you're going,

232
00:12:47,950 --> 00:12:49,750
