234
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,290
To organize something.

235
00:12:53,580 --> 00:12:54,420
Organize what?

236
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,660
Interesting exam questions.

237
00:12:57,450 --> 00:12:58,700
Wow.

238
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:00,330
