251
00:13:21,250 --> 00:13:22,540
Now there's this weird

252
00:13:22,540 --> 00:13:24,540
"bottoming out system".

253
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,290
But it's fine.

254
00:13:28,290 --> 00:13:29,910
Our Sheng is a real whiz.

255
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,290
He won't get kicked out of our class.

256
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:33,000
He's ranked 79.

257
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,160
That's risky though.

258
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:35,870
And

259
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:37,910
