260
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,120
saying he's bored.

261
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:41,610
Better give him something to do.

262
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:46,080
Hey, let me take this call.

263
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,040
Hello?

264
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,540
Yeah.

265
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:52,040
Okay. I'll go find you now.

266
00:13:52,330 --> 00:13:53,790
OK. OK.

267
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,540
I'm off then.

268
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,410
Where to?

269
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,660
- It's a secret.
- Another secret?

270
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:01,120
- Bye.
- Another secret, huh?

271
00:14:07,250 --> 00:14:08,120
Alright.

272
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,290
Press it again.

273
00:14:09,290 --> 00:14:10,330
Press it twice. Then it works.

274
00:14:10,330 --> 00:14:11,170
See you.

275
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,940
(Sticky Note)
Jiang Tian. Jiang Tian. Jiang Tian.

276
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:31,060
Yes.

277
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:33,810
(Sticky Note)
You said the dorm's out of power?

278
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,840
Has it come back yet?

279
00:14:36,930 --> 00:14:37,840
Not yet.

280
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:40,840
(Sticky Note)
And you said you had a plan tonight?

281
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:45,910
Yeah.

282
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:47,860
(Sticky Note)
What is it?

283
00:14:53,170 --> 00:14:54,370
Do you need to leave school?

284
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:04,900
Yes. I'll go to the Little White House.

285
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:10,030
(Sticky Note)
Then go ahead. I'll go eat.

286
00:15:15,930 --> 00:15:16,870
What are you going to do?

287
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:23,870
(Unread)

288
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,540
You're right on time.

289
00:15:45,540 --> 00:15:47,250
Let me update you
on this month's accounts.

290
00:15:47,540 --> 00:15:49,910
We're short 6,000 NT$ this month.

291
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:51,750
That's not a small amount.

292
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,080
What's going on?

293
00:15:53,290 --> 00:15:54,540
What are you rushing for?

294
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:58,620
I'm wondering if we didn't

295
00:15:58,950 --> 00:16:01,780
get the money from the last delivery.

296
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:04,520
What do you think?

297
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:07,290
Got you.

298
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:08,790
This time, you can't get away with it.

299
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:12,330
- Isn't this Jenny's kidnapping footage?
- Let me go.

300
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:13,340
Yeah.

301
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:15,750
It was really hard to find this footage.

302
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:17,500
Then the school had a power cut,

303
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:18,910
so I have to use your computer.

304
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,790
Is it that urgent

305
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:24,410
to check some footage?

306
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,540
I don't like to put things off.

307
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:32,160
You're just like Jenny,

308
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:35,330
getting impulsive when you're worked up.

309
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:37,120
That makes sense.

310
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:41,330
If I weren't impulsive,

311
00:16:41,330 --> 00:16:43,040
you might not be alive today, right?

312
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,660
This says "Please touch."

313
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:08,660
"Please touch"?

314
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:09,910
See? Come and look.

315
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:13,580
Yeah, "Please touch."

316
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:16,330
Here we go. D-o-g.

317
00:17:16,330 --> 00:17:17,290
Dog.

318
00:17:17,290 --> 00:17:18,620
Hey! What are you doing?

319
00:17:19,870 --> 00:17:20,910
None of your business.

320
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,370
This is a historic site.

321
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:24,120
A historic site? So?

322
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:25,450
It says "Do not touch",

323
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:26,290
but you keep touching it.

324
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:27,910
How is that important?

325
00:17:27,910 --> 00:17:29,330
Don't touch it.

326
00:17:29,330 --> 00:17:32,080
These things have witnessed
200 years of Tamsui's history.

327
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:34,700
Tamsui? What sway?

328
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:36,120
And you're littering
with cigarette butts.

329
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,580
What are you going to do about it?

330
00:17:37,870 --> 00:17:38,950
Please leave now.

331
00:17:38,950 --> 00:17:39,800
Say that again.

332
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,790
- Say that again.
- Please leave now.

333
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:42,000
Say it one more time.

334
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,950
Got a big group, so what?

335
00:17:49,370 --> 00:17:50,500
Not really.

336
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:51,700
Just one more person than you.

337
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:52,910
What do you want?

338
00:17:54,540 --> 00:17:55,870
What do you want?

339
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:11,950
Come back!

340
00:18:14,450 --> 00:18:15,700
- Don't run!
- Stay there!

341
00:18:18,370 --> 00:18:19,210
Don't run!

342
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:20,430
You heard me?

343
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:27,620
Don't run!

344
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,040
Let's go.

345
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,160
Come. Quickly.

346
00:18:53,290 --> 00:18:54,500
Good thing I ran into you.

347
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:56,700
I'm terrible at fighting.

348
00:18:56,700 --> 00:18:58,160
I'd have gotten beaten up badly.

349
00:19:01,910 --> 00:19:02,870
Thanks.

350
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:05,750
No worries.

351
00:19:14,580 --> 00:19:15,540
Do you also study at NTU?

352
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:16,830
Yeah.

353
00:19:17,870 --> 00:19:19,040
You too?

354
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,910
Senior, Physics.

355
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:25,200
History, sophomore.

356
00:19:26,580 --> 00:19:27,830
Do you like history?

357
00:19:27,830 --> 00:19:28,700
Yeah.

358
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:31,200
I'm working on a paper
about the history of this area.

359
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:32,790
So I'm here for field research.

360
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,290
What about you, senior?

361
00:19:35,790 --> 00:19:37,000
Do you like physics?

362
00:19:38,370 --> 00:19:40,410
I chose it because it lets me

363
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:42,120
see a different world.

364
00:19:42,540 --> 00:19:43,950
Also,

365
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,500
my dad doesn't get physics.

366
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:47,700
so knowing it is cool for me.

367
00:19:55,450 --> 00:19:57,750
Actually, I've always had a dream.

368
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,910
I want to open a coffee shop here

369
00:20:01,450 --> 00:20:03,120
and make my own history.

370
00:20:08,330 --> 00:20:10,040
That sounds awesome.

371
00:20:10,910 --> 00:20:11,870
Senior,

372
00:20:12,290 --> 00:20:13,700
if you do open it,

373
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,080
please count me in.

374
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:19,960
Deal.

375
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,290
Remember now?

376
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:41,700
You owe me a life, don't you?

377
00:20:42,910 --> 00:20:44,660
So I came back with you.

378
00:20:44,660 --> 00:20:45,620
We opened this shop together.

379
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,450
And I even work as your waiter.

380
00:20:49,290 --> 00:20:50,370
Did I force you to do that?

381
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:52,910
Do you know

382
00:20:53,410 --> 00:20:55,790
why I agreed to come back with you?

383
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:02,330
Let me take this call.

384
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:07,000
Hello, Jenny Yang?

385
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:09,620
Did you need something?

386
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:13,800
Okay.

387
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,450
Going shopping with me, huh?

388
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:29,330
I'd rather not, honestly.

389
00:21:29,330 --> 00:21:31,040
Really? I'll go back then.

390
00:21:31,700 --> 00:21:34,120
I tried so hard to ask you out,
but you ignored me.

391
00:21:34,120 --> 00:21:35,910
Eventually, I had to give up.

392
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:38,500
Thanks for giving up on me.

393
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:42,540
Now I like someone else.

394
00:21:42,540 --> 00:21:43,750
You were discarded.

395
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:45,790
Just do your job

396
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:48,000
and help me pick a gift for him.

397
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,910
Understand?

398
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,200
Yes.

399
00:21:53,370 --> 00:21:54,580
Hey, look.

400
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:55,790
What about this one?

401
00:21:56,870 --> 00:21:57,790
It has a flower pattern.

402
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:58,750
You want me to be honest?

403
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,600
Yeah.

404
00:21:59,610 --> 00:22:00,540
It sucks.

405
00:22:01,370 --> 00:22:04,540
Have you ever seen a guy
with something like this on his desk?

406
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:06,040
If you're giving a gift,
make it practical.

407
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:08,450
Something he can use every day.

408
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:11,540
Alright. You do have a good point.

409
00:22:17,250 --> 00:22:19,200
What about this? It's a cup.

410
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,040
What do you think?

411
00:22:21,410 --> 00:22:24,000
Do you mean no, or just don't know?

412
00:22:24,330 --> 00:22:25,500
I don't know.

413
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,330
Are you a guy or not?

414
00:22:27,330 --> 00:22:28,750
You can't even handle this?

415
00:22:28,750 --> 00:22:29,640
I'm a guy.

416
00:22:29,650 --> 00:22:32,750
But I don't know what your guy likes.

417
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,870
Think it over, okay?

418
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:48,080
Oh.

419
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:49,950
This is it.

420
00:22:49,950 --> 00:22:51,790
He'll love this cup.

421
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:22,020
(What are you going to do?)
(Unread)

422
00:23:40,470 --> 00:23:41,490
(Sticky Note)
I'm finished eating.

423
00:23:42,470 --> 00:23:44,960
How much longer will it take
to get your stuff done?

424
00:23:47,130 --> 00:23:47,970
I'm done.

425
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:51,020
(Sticky Note)
So soon?

426
00:23:54,520 --> 00:23:55,360
What's wrong?

427
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:58,560
(Sticky Note)
Nothing.

428
00:23:58,780 --> 00:24:00,180
Did you go back to school?

429
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:10,090
Not yet.

430
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:15,820
On my way.

431
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:24,100
(Sticky Note)

432
00:24:24,630 --> 00:24:25,580
What do you mean?

433
00:24:28,050 --> 00:24:28,970
(Sticky Note)
Where are you now?

434
00:24:40,190 --> 00:24:41,850
I'll be at the west gate
after I cross the road.

435
00:24:54,210 --> 00:24:55,430
(Sticky Note)
Are you really here?

436
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,520
How come I don't see you?

437
00:25:04,910 --> 00:25:08,620
The power's back on!

438
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:09,950
Hey, where are you going?

439
00:25:09,950 --> 00:25:10,830
Picking someone up.

440
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:12,160
Running so fast?

441
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:16,910
I'm gonna shower today.

442
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,160
Yay!

443
00:25:24,870 --> 00:25:25,830
Excuse me.

444
00:25:55,970 --> 00:25:57,020
Where are you?

445
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:04,620
Did you sneak over there...

446
00:26:05,330 --> 00:26:06,370
Or...

447
00:26:08,330 --> 00:26:09,580
You came from the dorm, didn't you?

448
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:10,580
You tricked me.

449
00:26:16,290 --> 00:26:17,330
Never mind.

450
00:26:17,330 --> 00:26:18,910
At least you showed up in time.

451
00:26:19,370 --> 00:26:20,500
I forgive you.

452
00:26:24,450 --> 00:26:26,000
So you can walk by yourself now?

453
00:26:27,080 --> 00:26:28,040
Yeah.

454
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:33,950
It's okay. I can do it...

455
00:26:34,370 --> 00:26:35,290
By myself.

456
00:26:47,290 --> 00:26:48,370
Who took you here?

457
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:51,500
Ms. Sun.

458
00:26:51,910 --> 00:26:53,790
I had to beg her a lot
before she finally agreed.

459
00:26:54,450 --> 00:26:55,540
Oh, you know what?

460
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:56,830
She's been making

461
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:58,910
pig's feet for me lately.

462
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,410
Most people get bone broth for injuries.

463
00:27:01,410 --> 00:27:03,370
But why does she
keep making pig's feet?

464
00:27:04,250 --> 00:27:06,200
You are what you eat.

465
00:27:06,790 --> 00:27:08,040
What's that supposed to mean?

466
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,410
Are you calling me a pig?

467
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:14,700
What? Have I...

468
00:27:14,700 --> 00:27:16,120
Have I changed in any way?

469
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:18,410
Yes.

470
00:27:19,120 --> 00:27:20,250
What is it?

471
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,080
You got fatter.

472
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,040
You...

473
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:31,440
♪I don't know how to keep you
from being confused♪

474
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,760
♪I thought you understood♪

475
00:27:33,830 --> 00:27:35,750
Why are you so afraid of gaining weight?

476
00:27:37,450 --> 00:27:39,040
Because you always call me fat.

477
00:27:41,080 --> 00:27:42,540
Fame portends trouble for men

478
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:43,830
just as

479
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:46,410
fattening does for pigs.

480
00:27:47,410 --> 00:27:49,000
Fine, stop calling me fat.

481
00:27:49,950 --> 00:27:51,370
I know you're still not fully healed.

482
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:55,520
♪Is just 17♪

483
00:27:55,540 --> 00:27:56,410
Give me your hand.

484
00:27:56,440 --> 00:28:01,180
♪The future is too far away♪

485
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,040
Let me help you.

486
00:28:02,050 --> 00:28:05,260
♪Let's run forward♪

487
00:28:05,330 --> 00:28:06,540
What's wrong?

488
00:28:09,910 --> 00:28:11,500
So it's true.

489
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:13,580
Students say a lot of couples

490
00:28:13,580 --> 00:28:14,660
come here to date.

491
00:28:19,410 --> 00:28:20,410
Let's go.

492
00:28:20,930 --> 00:28:27,650
♪A young man's heart
is a burning wasteland♪

493
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:31,290
Watch your step.

494
00:28:31,870 --> 00:28:33,450
If you fall, it's not on me.

495
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,200
You're holding me.

496
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,950
So if I fall, it's your fault.

497
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:44,580
No, I'm holding you,
so it's still your fault.

498
00:28:45,330 --> 00:28:47,410
Fine. It will be my fault.

499
00:28:58,660 --> 00:29:00,370
Sheng, you are back?

500
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:04,040
What? I'm not welcome?

501
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:06,500
Am I interrupting you guys
while you're living together?

502
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:09,540
No, of course not!

503
00:29:12,450 --> 00:29:15,160
So Tian rushed out
because you were coming?

504
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,790
- You know what...
- Aren't you going to shower?

505
00:29:17,580 --> 00:29:18,500
Just go.

506
00:29:20,410 --> 00:29:21,870
Yeah, I'll shower today.

507
00:29:21,870 --> 00:29:23,080
I stink.

508
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:25,750
Time for a shower.

509
00:29:29,410 --> 00:29:31,540
Wow, you really do stink.

510
00:29:31,540 --> 00:29:33,750
I just had charcoal hot pot.

511
00:29:49,830 --> 00:29:50,870
That was you.

512
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:52,870
What do you mean?

513
00:29:52,870 --> 00:29:55,750
I knew I had seen
that T-shirt somewhere.

514
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:56,910
I thought I was wrong back then.

515
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:58,950
Does it look good on me?

516
00:29:59,620 --> 00:30:01,660
Just now. On the second floor
at the west gate.

517
00:30:03,790 --> 00:30:04,790
Oh...

518
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,040
Oh?

519
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:08,500
I know.

520
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:10,790
I went to see He Shi...

521
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:13,080
Actually, we had something
to take care of.

522
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:15,750
Okay. Don't be nervous.

523
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:16,700
I'm not interrogating you.

524
00:30:16,700 --> 00:30:18,290
No. I'm not nervous.

525
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:21,450
What about you?

526
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,250
Why were you there?

527
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:27,580
Why did you go to the dating hotspot?

528
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:31,200
Who tricked you into going there?

529
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:33,830
He was heading back to school.

530
00:30:33,830 --> 00:30:35,540
Tian went to pick him up.

531
00:30:36,370 --> 00:30:37,330
Oh.

532
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:39,200
I thought he went there
for the same reason.

533
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:43,120
The power's back on.

534
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:44,200
I'll take a shower.

535
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:46,700
Wait, wait.

536
00:30:46,950 --> 00:30:48,290
What did you just say?

537
00:30:48,950 --> 00:30:50,580
"The same reason"?

538
00:30:52,330 --> 00:30:54,040
What were you doing
at the dating hotspot?

539
00:30:55,780 --> 00:30:56,620
Did you...

540
00:30:56,620 --> 00:30:58,040
I'm off to shower.

541
00:30:58,040 --> 00:30:59,700
Hey! I should be the first...

542
00:31:04,910 --> 00:31:05,870
Hey.

543
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:08,330
Should we remind him?

544
00:31:08,330 --> 00:31:09,500
Of what?

545
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:13,120
Being in a relationship
will mess with his studies.

546
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:17,410
Teachers can say that to him.

547
00:31:17,410 --> 00:31:19,660
But if you tell him that,

548
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,200
you might get punched.

549
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,290
That's right.

550
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:28,790
But as Shi's best buddy,

551
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,450
I think I should tell him that.

552
00:31:32,370 --> 00:31:35,080
To be, or not to be,

553
00:31:35,790 --> 00:31:37,080
what should I do?

554
00:31:37,660 --> 00:31:39,620
- Go away, you bumpkin. You stink.
- What should I do?

555
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:40,660
Go away.

556
00:31:43,370 --> 00:31:45,080
What are you doing?

557
00:31:46,410 --> 00:31:47,500
All set.

558
00:31:47,830 --> 00:31:48,870
Let's switch beds.

559
00:31:49,250 --> 00:31:50,410
You're sleeping in my bed.

560
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,250
I made it to the fifth floor.

561
00:31:52,250 --> 00:31:53,540
Do you think I can't handle these steps?

562
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:55,580
Do you think I'm asking
for your opinion?

563
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:58,700
And you can take off your bandages now.

564
00:31:59,870 --> 00:32:01,330
What should I change into?

565
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:04,000
